title: Chance Of a Lifetime 1950 B/W

Chance of a Lifetime (1950) 

  89 min   -  Drama  -  14 March 1951 (USA





 



The workers in a small plough factory take over the firm, but when a large order falls through, the old management come back to help out.


Director: Bernard Miles 

Writers: Walter Greenwood (original screenplay), Bernard Miles (original screenplay) 

Stars: Basil Radford, Niall MacGinnis, Bernard Miles
